ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.TEvaSet
ScalarVariable.description: Set point for leaving chilled water temperature

Data.equation: heaPum.equationfit.TEvaSet = heaPum.TEvaSet = TSetCoo.offset+(if time < TSetCoo.startTime then 0 else (if time < TSetCoo.startTime+TSetCoo.duration then (time-TSetCoo.startTime)*TSetCoo.height/TSetCoo.duration else TSetCoo.height));

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.TConSet
ScalarVariable.description: Set point for leaving heating water temperature

Data.equation: heaPum.equationfit.TConSet = heaPum.TConSet = TSetHea.offset+(if time < TSetHea.startTime then 0 else (if time < TSetHea.startTime+TSetHea.duration then (time-TSetHea.startTime)*TSetHea.height/TSetHea.duration else TSetHea.height));

heaPum.equationfit.CLR = (if heaPum.uMod == 1 then 0 else (if heaPum.uMod == 0 then 0 else heaPum.equationfit.A1[1]*heaPum.equationfit.x1[1]+heaPum.equationfit.A1[2]*heaPum.equationfit.x1[2]+heaPum.equationfit.A1[3]*heaPum.equationfit.x1[3]+heaPum.equationfit.A1[4]*heaPum.equationfit.x1[4]+heaPum.equationfit.A1[5]*heaPum.equationfit.x1[5]));

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.P_HD
ScalarVariable.description: Power Ratio in heating dominanat mode

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.P_CD
ScalarVariable.description: Power Ratio in cooling dominant mode

Data.equation: heaPum.equationfit.P_CD = (if heaPum.uMod == 1 then 0 else (if heaPum.uMod == 0 then 0 else heaPum.equationfit.A2[1]*heaPum.equationfit.x2[1]+heaPum.equationfit.A2[2]*heaPum.equationfit.x2[2]+heaPum.equationfit.A2[3]*heaPum.equationfit.x2[3]+heaPum.equationfit.A2[4]*heaPum.equationfit.x2[4]+heaPum.equationfit.A2[5]*heaPum.equationfit.x2[5]));

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.QCon_flow_ava
ScalarVariable.description: Heating capacity available at the condender

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.QEva_flow_ava
ScalarVariable.description: Cooling capacity available at the Evaporator

Data.equation: heaPum.equationfit.QEva_flow_ava = (if heaPum.uMod == 1 then 0 else (if heaPum.uMod == 0 then 0 else heaPum.equationfit.CLR*heaPum.equationfit.QEva_heatflow_nominal));

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.per.nCLR
ScalarVariable.description: Number of coefficients for Cooling load Ratio

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.per.nPowR_CD
ScalarVariable.description: Number of coefficients for Power Ratio

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.VCon_flow_nominal
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Condenser volume flow rate nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.mCon_flow_nominal
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Condenser mass flow rate nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.VEva_flow_nominal
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Condenser volume flow rate nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.mEva_flow_nominal
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Evaporator mass flow rate nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.PCon_nominal_HD
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Compressor Power nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.PEva_nominal_CD
ScalarVariable.description: Heating mode Compressor Power nominal capacity

ScalarVariable.name: heaPum.equationfit.Q_flow_small
ScalarVariable.description: Small value for heat flow rate or power, used to avoid division by zero

Data.equation: heaPum.equationfit.P = heaPum.P = (if heaPum.uMod == 1 then heaPum.equationfit.P_HD*heaPum.equationfit.PCon_nominal_HD else (if heaPum.uMod == 0 then 0 else heaPum.equationfit.P_CD*heaPum.equationfit.PEva_nominal_CD));

heaPum.equationfit.QCon_flow_Set = smooth(1, smooth(1, (if noEvent(1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)-heaPum.Q_flow_small > heaPum.Q_flow_small/10) then 1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow) else (if noEvent(1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)-heaPum.Q_flow_small < -heaPum.Q_flow_small/10) then heaPum.Q_flow_small else (if heaPum.Q_flow_small/10 > 0 then 2.5*((1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)-heaPum.Q_flow_small)*((10*(1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)-heaPum.Q_flow_small)/heaPum.Q_flow_small)^2-3)*(heaPum.Q_flow_small-1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)))/heaPum.Q_flow_small+0.5*(1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)+heaPum.Q_flow_small) else 0.5*(1.893*(heaPum.hSet_Con.y-conPum.ports[1].h_outflow)+heaPum.Q_flow_small))))));
